{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Saltwater Bodies is a cave-diving body horror game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore underwater cave systems beneath a salt flat, and nurture an unnatural vessel away from prying eyes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features a physics-based caving system where you have to be mindful of positioning your body parts, and balance that against holding your breath underwater - Is it worth breathing out precious air to squeeze through a smaller gap?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Outside of underwater caves you can socialize with co-workers and perform arcane experiments to construct yourself a new vessel. A branching narrative that depends on how you balance your day job and your more supernatural contracts...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game uses a retro style with vertex wobble and a lowered resolution. These can be adjusted in the settings if it's not your jam!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3368150?t=1740769463","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368150/ea69a71748d6b4a0763e52bb81bdbee79fb93d8c/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740769463","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368150/ab2d1f0b2150fbd5dd6ee41552ce67bff6b4a9b8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740769463","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368150/ab2d1f0b2150fbd5dd6ee41552ce67bff6b4a9b8/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740769463","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,2,5],"notes":"Depictions of drug use. Medical and non-medical gore. Intentional and accidental death/killing."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Saltwater Bodies is a cave-diving body horror game.</p><p class